135
00:06:47,803 --> 00:06:48,683
But I just ran with it.

136
00:06:49,283 --> 00:06:51,744
And to me, it was more important to pick something and stick

137
00:06:51,804 --> 00:06:56,086
with it than to be completely technically

138
00:06:56,226 --> 00:06:58,967
accurate with the retro aesthetic

139
00:06:58,987 --> 00:06:59,807
that I was trying to achieve.

140
00:07:01,339 --> 00:07:03,820
So I throttled the game's FPS to 15.

141
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,660
That helped me in the animation process,

142
00:07:05,780 --> 00:07:08,301
