299
00:14:35,048 --> 00:14:37,129
that fall into the uncanny valley.

300
00:14:37,669 --> 00:14:39,510
We naturally get uncomfortable watching

301
00:14:39,570 --> 00:14:40,670
things that move like us.

302
00:14:41,491 --> 00:14:43,231
And the animated monstrosities in Faith

303
00:14:43,291 --> 00:14:45,812
have this uncanny quality because they're

304
00:14:45,832 --> 00:14:47,393
based on real human performances.

305
00:14:58,217 --> 00:14:58,477
It me.

