380
00:18:44,368 --> 00:18:48,570
But if you don't have the means to work with cutting-edge graphics or the time or the patience,

381
00:18:49,251 --> 00:18:52,453
your visual design can still contribute to a feeling of horror.

382
00:18:53,313 --> 00:18:56,775
I just stuck to one aesthetic and working within my constraints.

383
00:18:57,496 --> 00:19:00,238
I had a lot of fun with it, and I think it turned out pretty compelling.

384
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:06,041
