00:25:16,674 --> 00:25:16,915
And so...

520
00:25:21,119 --> 00:25:23,341
What I do is I think of things that would scare me.

521
00:25:23,361 --> 00:25:26,265
I personally am terrified of supernatural horror

522
00:25:26,445 --> 00:25:28,908
and kind of this religious horror, not just Christian,

523
00:25:28,968 --> 00:25:31,791
but there's exorcism stories from other religions

524
00:25:31,831 --> 00:25:32,832
that would blow your mind.

525
00:25:32,872 --> 00:25:33,393
They're insane.

