00:25:33,413 --> 00:25:35,375
I wish we would make more multimedia about it.

527
00:25:35,395 --> 00:25:36,356
So.

528
00:25:38,855 --> 00:25:41,696
My person, a lot of my personal tastes come into play.

529
00:25:41,836 --> 00:25:43,037
I prefer a sense of dread.

530
00:25:43,177 --> 00:25:45,397
If I watch a movie or play a game and then I drive home

531
00:25:45,517 --> 00:25:48,478
and I'm scared to look behind me in the back seat at night,

532
00:25:48,939 --> 00:25:50,939
then I kind of log that away in the back of my mind.

533
00:25:50,979 --> 00:25:52,580
I'm like, I want to do something like that.

534
00:25:53,360 --> 00:25:56,601
And sometimes it's hard not to copy directly

535
00:25:56,681 --> 00:25:58,502
