541
00:26:16,086 --> 00:26:18,127
And then I do my overlay wall pass

542
00:26:18,307 --> 00:26:21,827
for things that are layered up on top of the player.

543
00:26:21,927 --> 00:26:24,128
And then I do my collision pass, where I kind of paint in

544
00:26:24,728 --> 00:26:26,268
where you're not supposed to walk.

545
00:26:26,929 --> 00:26:28,629
And then that gets thrown into GameMaker.

546
00:26:28,709 --> 00:26:29,429
I use GameMaker.

547
00:26:30,209 --> 00:26:32,470
And the scares are a lot of iteration.

